In a large pot with boiling salted water cook egg noodles until al dente. Drain. In a large bowl mix together the cottage cheese, sour cream, minced onion, garlic, Worcestershire sauce, red pepper sauce, and salt. Stir in cooked egg noodles. Pour into a greased 2 quart casserole dish. Bake in a preheated 350 degree F (175 degrees C) for 30 minutes, or until heated through and bubbly. Serve warm.